---
---

<section id="about" class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="avatar-box">
        <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/143915664?v=4&s=160" alt="周硕" width="160" height="160" loading="eager" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="greeting">你好，我是</p>
      <h1 class="name">周硕</h1>
      <p class="title-role">
        &gt; <span class="typing-text">Java 后端开发实习生</span><span class="cursor">_</span>
      </p>
      <p class="bio">
        湖南科技大学 数据科学与大数据技术 本科在读。
        专注于 Java 后端与 AI 应用开发，
        擅长 Spring Cloud 微服务架构与大模型工程化落地。
        活跃的开源贡献者，向 Spring AI Alibaba、Spring Cloud Alibaba 等项目提交过 PR。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://github.com/zshs000" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-ghost">查看项目</a>
      </div>
      <blockquote class="quote">
        <p>"Controlling complexity is the essence of computer programming."</p>
        <cite>— Brian Kernighan</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .avatar-box {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--bg-white);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hard-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .avatar-box img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .greeting {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .name {
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .title-role {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cursor { animation: blink 1s step-end infinite; }
  @keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }

  .bio {
    max-width: 500px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--text);
    color: var(--bg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hard);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-accent);
    transform: translate(2px, 2px);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: var(--bg-white);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hard);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .quote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .quote p {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .quote cite {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .name { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    .avatar-box { width: 120px; height: 120px; }
    .bio { margin: 0 auto 1.75rem; }
    .hero-actions { justify-content: center; }
    .quote { margin: 0 auto; }
  }
</style>
